summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 226W, page 15 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Tax Lot 398, Tax Lot 94, Tax Lot 290, north 140' of Tax lot 113, and Tax Lot 190, all in Sec. 29-26-4, from Duplex Residence Medium Density (RD7200) Zone to Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone, located 95 ft. east from the southeast corner of Meridian Ave. and No. 110th St.
